Supply6

ABOUT

Supply6 is a renowned brand that specializes in providing nutrition products designed to meet the needs of individuals leading busy lifestyles. Their flagship product, Supply6 360, is a comprehensive nutrition solution that offers a convenient and effective way to achieve optimal health and wellness. With a potent blend of essential vitamins, minerals, adaptogens, probiotics, berries, and greens, Supply6 360 aims to enhance overall well-being, making it the perfect addition to your morning routine.

SCOPE

  • Web UI/UX
  • Shopify
  • Photography
  • Video Production

INDUSTRY

Nutrition - D2C

CHALLENGES

Capturing
The Essence

01

To position Supply 6 360 as a credible and reliable nutrition product.

02

Blending aesthetics with the functionality
of the product.

03

Effectively communicating the value proposition
of the product.

04

Making the website experience seamless.

SOLUTION

Communicating
The Vision

The website was carefully designed to create a user-friendly interface that guides visitors effortlessly through the product offerings, benefits, and purchasing options. Every aspect, from intuitive navigation to visually appealing layouts, is optimized to provide a seamless experience that encourages exploration, engagement, and ultimately, more purchases. We prioritized the use of high-quality visuals throughout the website. Through stunning imagery, we effectively communicated the brand’s commitment to providing nutritionally dense offerings that support a healthy lifestyle.

Intuitive
 & Efficient

WEBSITE UI/UX

The website design was carefully crafted, with clean and modern aesthetics that reflect the brand’s professionalism and passion for nutrition.

Facilitating Easy &
 Efficient Purchases

We streamlined Supply 6’s checkout process, minimizing any unnecessary steps and ensuring a smooth transaction. The website experience extends beyond the transactional aspect, prioritizing customer engagement and interaction. We incorporated interactive elements such as chat support, allowing customers to seek immediate assistance and clarification on any queries they may have.

Compelling Narratives
 & Engaging Visuals

PHOTOGRAPHY & VIDEOGRAPHY

The lifestyle shots were designed to create a relatable and aspirational image of the products, while the product shots were aimed at showcasing the key aspects of the product itself. We also created several engaging videos that highlight the product, its features, and its unique selling points (USPs).

IMPACT

A Resounding
Success

Supply6’s product launch was an exceptional success, fueled by a combination of a clean and intuitive website design, captivating concept videos and images used as advertisements. The positive user experience, enabled by the well-designed website, created a seamless pathway for visitors to explore the brand’s offerings. The concept videos and images served as powerful marketing tools, attracting a significant influx of traffic and driving impressive sales.
